    public class SeleniumBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
implements br.ufmg.dcc.saotome.beholder.builder.Builder
    This class is a implementation of Builder interface to create all the objects used to execute a test case. All objects uses Selenium-Webdriver to find the component and interact with a web browser, simulating actions of a system user.
